                     <interp inst="t18410823-2271-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">GUILTY</hi>. Aged 24.—<hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to mercy on account of the provocation.</hi>
                  </rs>—
